{
  "stem": "11998.2",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I, I must say that they-- we were very much frightened.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "There was-- this was mainly old Jews that, that they went after.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And the young people, they took and they very quickly organized into work parties.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And they deported most of the young people very, very quickly.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "My father was deported when I came back from Lodz in October, on October the 16th, 1939.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "They, they went to the Jewish community in Chorzow.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And they told them that they must-- all the men between the ages of 16 and 45 or 50 must come to a certain place to go to be sent to labor, to come with winter clothes and picks and shovels, and that they're going to go and go to some work camp.",
      "word_count": 53
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And my father, of course, went, and-- [PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] was sent away.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And I was-- I remember distinctly as it was yesterday how upset I was and I saw-- when I saw my father [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] being taken away on a, on a truck.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And I didn't think that I'll see him again.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And he was gone for many months before he came back.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "My, my grandfather, yes-- my grandfather, my mother, and my sister, and I we went from Lodz.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We went-- we had permission to go by train back to, to Chorzow.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But even then, even so we had permission to go, maybe didn't have-- we didn't have any papers.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But we were on a-- in a cattle car.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And every, every time the station-- the, the train pulled into a station and stopped, the Nazis would come onto the train and call for any Juden.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Are they any Jews there?",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
